    "body":  "﻿Codex review: APPROVED for closeout.\n\nReviewed commit `22ba83d` against the approved `MENUBAR-FILE-SUBSTRATE` TASK packet. Scope is exactly `crates/editor-egui-host/src/handoff.rs` + `crates/editor-egui-host/src/lib.rs`; no `Cargo.toml` or `editor-shell` changes. The implementation uses a dedicated bounded FIFO `MenuCommandHandoff`, reuses `editor-ui::menus::Command`, and keeps Dispatch A honest as visible + enqueue-only until Dispatch B drains/routes the queue.\n\nVerification re-run locally from detached `22ba83d`:\n- `cargo test -p rge-editor-egui-host --lib` passed (16/16, including the 4 new menu/handoff tests).\n- `.ai/dispatch.verify.ps1` with `RUST_TEST_THREADS=2` exited 0; architecture lints passed 10/10.\n- `git diff --check` clean; no `Cargo.toml` diff.\n\nLive PR checks: all 13 passed.\n\nDurable review packet filed: `ai_handoffs/MENUBAR-FILE-SUBSTRATE_REVIEW_2026-06-01_23-36-18+0300.md`.\n\nNo correction items. Merge remains gated on explicit human authorization.\r\n",
